text: Attock District () is a district in the Punjab province of Pakistan. == Administration == The district of Attock is administratively subdivided into six tehsils, each with an elected Nazim: * Attock Tehsil * Fateh Jang Tehsil * Hasan Abdal Tehsil * Jand Tehsil * Pindi Gheb Tehsil * Hazro Tehsil Category:Rawalpindi Division
title: Attock District
